# =============================================================================
# Misc files
# =============================================================================
# Note: Avoid blanket *.txt exclusion to preserve important documentation

# Exclude specific temporary/test text files
QobuzCLI/*-test.txt
QobuzCLI/build.log
QobuzCLI/output.log
QobuzCLI/fresh-*.txt
QobuzCLI/simple-*.txt
QobuzCLI/single-*.txt
QobuzCLI/dashboard-test.txt
QobuzCLI/metadata-test.txt
QobuzCLI/bach-test.txt
scripts/*.txt

